channelName: Dave Hanson / Hey there, Dave here.
channelDescription:
Hey there! I’m Dave Hanson. I’m a tech founder turned investor turned YouTuber living in Dallas, Texas. This channel is all about personal finance, investing, credit cards... and occasionally other random stuff.

For me, financial minimalism means using the absolute least amount of time or effort to maximize how my money works for me. 

I’m not a financial advisor. I don’t have any courses to sell. I’m just a guy on the internet who retired in my 30’s and makes YouTube videos as a hobby. Hopefully, I can help encourage and educate the next generation of entrepreneurs and investors.

If any of that sounds interesting to you, consider subscribing!

Be sure to also check out my Dumb Money channels for startup investing and stock market videos.
